A light-emitting silicon alloy has been awarded "Breakthrough of the Year” by @PhysicsWorld. The material, developed @UniJena @TUeindhoven together with @jkulinz @TU_Muenchen, paves the way for silicon lasers that could lead to photon-based computers.
